title: People Holding Hands Dark Skin Tone Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a couple or friends holding hands, with one person having a dark skin tone and the other a light skin tone. It signifies connection, unity, and relationships.

The realistic texture and subtle highlights on each hand, rendered with Apple’s precise 3D design, convey a strong sense of support and connection.
